T02TD3245E:11a-1: dz'am gu l'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD3245E:11a-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho ga'i rim pas rang nyid kyi snying ga'i dkyil 'khor dmar por yi ge dz'am gi ye shes nges par rdzogs pa las rig pa'i mtshan du gyur ba ni dug sel ma ste /
T02TD3245E:11b-0: sku mdog ser mo gdengs ka bdun gyi kun nas @11b longs spyod pa 'bar bar gyur pa'i rin po che dam pas brgyan pa /
T02TD3245E:11b-3: rol pas bskyod pa dbu la mi bskyod pa legs par bzhugs pa gzhon nu ma'i mdun nyid kyis mchog tu 'bar bar gyur ba khro ba dang bcas pa'i bzhad pa nyid dang sbrul gyi smad ka dang ldan pa /
T02TD3245E:11b-4: g-yas pa'i phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
T02TD3245E:11b-5: gnyis pas ral gri gdengs par mdzad //
T02TD3245E:11b-6: gsum pa gar gyi stangs kyis 'dud //
T02TD3245E:11b-7: skrag mdzad mda' ni gsor bar mdzad //
T02TD3245E:11b-8: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub zhags pa ste //
T02TD3245E:11b-9: gnyis pa dug gi me tog can //
T02TD3245E:11b-10: gsum pa'i phyag na gzhu bsnams shing //
T02TD3245E:11b-11: smad ka la ni me tog ldan //
T02TD3245E:11b-12: padma'i gdan la bzhugs pa gser gyi mdog dang ldan zhing 'od dmar po'i dkyil 'khor las 'od zer spro bar mdzad ba /
T02TD3245E:11b-13: dri ma med pa'i 'ja' tshon 'bar bas nye 'khor yongs su khyab pa /
T02TD3245E:11b-14: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho'i sku rnams spro bar mdzad cing rang gi phyag na zla ba dang bum pa dang ldan pas dug gis zin pa nyal ba la 'khru bar mdzad pa /
T02TD3245E:11b-15: kha la yi ge dz'am gis brgyan pa ste /
T02TD3245E:11b-16: sku gsum dug sel rtag par yang //
T02TD3245E:11b-17: dug gis zin la bsgom par bya //
T02TD3245E:11b-18: gang phyir de ltar bsgoms gyur pas //
T02TD3245E:11b-19: ring min byang chub sems dpa' thob //
T02TD3245E:11b-20: lag pa gnyis sprul za ba'i rnam pas spyi bo nas 'gebs par byed pa /
T02TD3245E:11b-21: gdugs ltar byas pa ni dug sel ma'i phyag rgya'o //
T02TD3245E:11b-23: aom na ma:shar ku m'a ri ye tsur tstsha ts'a ti ts'a la ya tsu tstsha la ya sam ghatta ni m'a tt'am gi ai da biddhe aa he aom dz'a:sv'a h'a /
T02TD3245E:11b-24: 'phags ma dug sel ma'i sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3245E:11b-26: // / mkhas pa aa bha ya las dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
